summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of unplatted property in the northwest quarter of the southwest quarter of Section 23-25-3; Lots 8 and 9, Block 33, D. T. Denny's Home Addition; the easterly 60 feet of Lots 6 and 7, Block 80, Terry's 2nd Addition; Lots 10, 11 and 12, Harper's Addition; the west 50 feet of Lot 1, Block 10, Gilman's Addition; the south 20 feet of the east 60 feet of Lot 5 and the east 60 feet of Lot 6, Block 137, A. A. Denny's Broadway Addition; and Lots 21 to 24 inclusive, Block 60, Boston Company's Plat of West Seattle; with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-225 and 17-170, respectively.
